  • Method Details

    • setControllerBuilderMethods

      public static void setControllerBuilderMethods(HashMap<Class<?>,javafx.util.Callback<Class<?>,Object>> newControllerBuilderMethods)
      Sets a list of builder methods this screen navigator will use to build controllers with injected dependencies. NOTE: These methods MUST be specified before switching to any screens, or the application will crash because the screen navigator doesn't know how to build the controllers for each screen.
